'''Ulo uka''' bu ebee nde di ekpee chi di bia ha kpe-ekpere wo. Na mbu, ha dila ekpe ebee masiri wo n'ezi, du mgbe ha bidoro i ''buildu'' ulo uka. Aha ha ji a mata ulo uka wo gbasaa wo: ndi [[Islam]] na kpo ulo uka wo ''mosque'', ndi [[Jew]] a kpo nke ha, ''synagogue''. Dika ndena, ndi ekpere chi Jesus - [[Christian|ndi Christians]] - nwere aha ha ji a mata ulo uka wo.

Aha ha na kpo ya nwere ike bu ''church'', ma ''temple'', m'obu ''chapel'', ma otu nde ''Catholic'' ma ndi ''Orthodox'' na kpo nke wo: cathedral.

